r\u0101rangi: He kohinga taonga kua ota, whakarereketia
whakatakotoria: He kohinga kore raupapa o nga huānga ahurei
papakupu: He momo raraunga rite-JSON me nga takirua matua me te uara
tuple: He momo raraunga raupapa kua raupapa, kua tohua, kua kore e taea te huri
kahore: He tohu mo te kore uara
hoki mai: Ka whakahokia he uara mai i tetahi mahi
hua: Ka huri i tetahi taumahi ki te mahi whakangao (he kaitahuri me te kaitahuri)
haere: He korero whai waahi kaore he mahi
haere tonu: Ka hīkoi ki te whitiwhitinga e whai ake nei o te koropiko
ka mutu: Me mahi i muri i te piro/haunga te poraka ahakoa i mau he hapa, kaore ranei
ao: Ka whakapuaki i tetahi taurangi kia whai whanui te ao
kore rohe: Ka whakapuaki i tetahi taurangi no tetahi mahi o waho
tamata: Ka timata te poraka o te waehere me te whakahaere hapa
h\u0101unga: Ka hopu me te hapai i nga tuunga motuhake
whakapae: Ka arotake i tetahi korero ka whakaara ake he hapa mena he he
me: Ka whakamahia mo nga kaiwhakahaere horopaki ki te whakahaere rauemi
